text: HDNet Movies is an American digital cable and satellite television network. It is owned and operated by HDNet LLC, operating as a subsidiary of AXS TV LLC. It features theatrically released films and documentaries, which are presented in high definition and without commercial interruption or editing for content. It was launched in 2001. As of fall 2024, movies now have frequent commercial interruptions and are censored for content. Category:American television channels Category:2003 establishments in the United States
title: HDNet Movies
